2026-05-14T06:17:15.9431420Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9432086Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9433167Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9433983Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9434821Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9435658Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9436484Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9437308Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9438104Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T06:17:15.9438720Z 32    -->
